instruction: Design a website layout for a travel booking platform.
output: The website should be simple and easy to navigate, with the main elements of the website displaying prominently on the home page. The layout should include elements such as a search bar, categories of travel options, and a list of featured deals. Users should also be able to easily view their previously-saved trips, or access account settings to update their information or payment methods. The fonts, colors and images used should be modern and relevant to the travel and booking industry.
